{"tid":2299581,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大埔楊手足因遊蕩被判監九個月 今於高院獲准上訴期間保釋","createTime":"2020-11-25T01:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T03:03:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5ae4355d2720ef34574cb6838ce637189639475f","tid":2299581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T01:55:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F11564&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=562df2c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/11564</a><br />\n#高等法院第十四庭<br />\n#游德康暫委法官<br />\n#1226大埔 #上訴期間申請保釋<br />\n<br />\n👤楊(36)🛑服刑中 <br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n(1)遊蕩導致他人擔心<br />\n（令付賽珍擔心）<br />\n(2)阻撓在正當執行職務的警務人員<br />\n（警員20359）<br />\n<br />\n背景：經審訊後，控罪二表面證供不成立，控罪一於11月10日被#陳炳宙裁判官裁定罪名成立，判處即時監禁9個月，申請上訴期間保釋被拒。（詳情：審訊、審訊2、裁決、判刑）<br />\n<br />\n✅法庭批准被告上訴期間保釋✅<br />\n保釋條件如下：<br />\n擔保金$50000。<br />\n交出所有旅遊證件，不得離港。<br />\n在提供地址居住。<br />\n宵禁（11pm-7am）。<br />\n每週兩次報到警署。"},{"pid":"0045e571521eb3dc9ff1849b2a92738719e781b1","tid":2299581,"uid":47658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95da320edc0f1ce4d2f6844d674e9d4ea46c59f6","tid":2299581,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb829eec52ba5ae89313273ec05d31851637e93a","tid":2299581,"uid":27122,"l